        <!--Main block with description text and unsorted lists -->
        <article>
        <h2> Important dates </h2>
        <ul>
        <li>Born in Sambir, Lviv region, Ukrainian SSR, Soviet Union in 1968</li>
        <li>In 2000 Andriy became a presenter of his own hit parade "Hot Seven", which existed until 2002. </li>
        <li> Approximately starting from 2003 Andriy Kuzmenko works as a presenter of the program "Chance" and "Shikanemo" with the singer Natalia Mogilevska.</li>
        <li>Actor: Evenings in khutir near Dykanka (2001) — Kuzma, a friend of Vakula</li>
        <li>
            Actor: Lesya+Roma (2006) — as himself (cameo)</li>
        <li>Actor: Carnival night at Inter (2006) — as himself </li>
        <li> Actor: Very New Year Cinema (2007) — guest at the New Year Holiday in museum (cameo) </li>
        <li> Actor: Little Red Riding Hood (2009) — Blue Beard </li>
        <li>On February 2, 2015 around 8:20 Andriy died in a car accident near Lozuvatka village in Kryvyi Rih Raion in Dnipropetrovsk Oblast.</li>
        </ul>
        </article>
